entries.journal_entry_description: Deliver the contraband to the fence in the allotted time.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Rolo in the allotted time.  For this assignment you must avoid using any methods of travel other than on the ground, the authorities watch the travel terminals and shuttleports like a hawk.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Daren in the allotted time.  For this assignment you must avoid using any methods of travel other than on the ground, the authorities watch the travel terminals and shuttleports like a hawk.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Lennox in the allotted time. For this assignment you must avoid using any methods of travel other than on the ground, the authorities watch the travel terminals and shuttleports like a hawk.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Kirby in the allotted time.  Kirby is located on Dathomir. For this assignment you will have to launch into space and hyperspace to the Dathomir system.  If you try to travel directly using your ship the authorities are sure to catch you.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Lavina in the allotted time.  Lavina is located on Endor. For this assignment you will have to launch into space and hyperspace to the Endor system.  If you try to travel directly using your ship the authorities are sure to catch you.
entries.task07_comm_message_text: I thought you were the best of the best. I only deal with the elite in the smuggeling profession. Perhaps I should stop dealing with you.
